give @s written_book[written_book_content={title:"Totem Rituals Guide",author:"Ancient Ritualist",generation:0,pages:['Totem Rituals\n\nWelcome Ritualist!\n\nThis guide teaches the ancient art of totem magic.\n\nPress L for the full Advancement Guide!','Getting Started\n\n1. Craft a totem\n2. Sneak + right-click to place\n3. Right-click with an item\n4. Magic activates!\n\nSingle Totem Mode\n\nAll rituals work with just ONE totem by default!','Totem Tiers\n\n1. Wood - Basic\n   Range: 2x2x6\n2. Copper - Improved\n   Range: 3x3x8\n3. Iron - Strong\n   Range: 4x4x10\n4. Gold - Very Strong\n   Range: 5x5x12','Tiers Continued\n\n5. Diamond - Powerful\n   Range: 6x6x14\n6. Netherite - Ultimate\n   Range: 7x7x16\n\nHigher tier = larger range and stronger effects!','Ritual Effects\n\nPlace items on totems:\n\nEmerald - Growth\nGrows crops nearby\n\nDiamond - Strength\nBuffs players\n\nGold Ingot - Prosperity\nAttracts items + XP','More Effects\n\nIron Ingot - Protection\nDamages hostile mobs\n\nNether Star - Healing\nHeals players & animals\n\nArrow - Sentry\nFires at hostiles\nHas 2x range!','Crafting: Wood Totem\n\n┌───┬───┬───┐\n│   │ S │   │\n├───┼───┼───┤\n│ S │ P │ S │\n├───┼───┼───┤\n│   │ P │   │\n└───┴───┴───┘\n\nS = Stick\nP = Oak Planks\n\nResult: 1 Wood Totem','Crafting: Copper Totem\n\n┌───┬───┬───┐\n│   │ C │   │\n├───┼───┼───┤\n│ C │ B │ C │\n├───┼───┼───┤\n│   │ B │   │\n└───┴───┴───┘\n\nC = Copper Ingot\nB = Copper Block\n\nResult: 1 Copper Totem','Crafting: Iron Totem\n\n┌───┬───┬───┐\n│   │ I │   │\n├───┼───┼───┤\n│ I │ B │ I │\n├───┼───┼───┤\n│   │ B │   │\n└───┴───┴───┘\n\nI = Iron Ingot\nB = Iron Block\n\nResult: 1 Iron Totem','Crafting: Gold Totem\n\n┌───┬───┬───┐\n│   │ G │   │\n├───┼───┼───┤\n│ G │ B │ G │\n├───┼───┼───┤\n│   │ B │   │\n└───┴───┴───┘\n\nG = Gold Ingot\nB = Gold Block\n\nResult: 1 Gold Totem','Crafting: Diamond Totem\n\n┌───┬───┬───┐\n│   │ D │   │\n├───┼───┼───┤\n│ D │ B │ D │\n├───┼───┼───┤\n│   │ B │   │\n└───┴───┴───┘\n\nD = Diamond\nB = Diamond Block\n\nResult: 1 Diamond Totem','Crafting: Netherite Totem\n\n┌───┬───┬───┐\n│   │ N │   │\n├───┼───┼───┤\n│ N │ B │ N │\n├───┼───┼───┤\n│   │ B │   │\n└───┴───┴───┘\n\nN = Netherite Ingot\nB = Netherite Block\n\nResult: 1 Netherite','Crafting: Ritual Paste\n\nShapeless Recipe:\n\n3x Wheat\n1x Water Bucket\n1x Short Grass\n\nResult: 4 Paste\n\nUsed for Upgrade Slates','Crafting: Upgrade Slate\n\n┌───┬───┬───┐\n│ P │   │ P │\n├───┼───┼───┤\n│   │ T │   │\n├───┼───┼───┤\n│ P │   │ P │\n└───┴───┴───┘\n\nP = Paste\nT = Totem Base\n\nMake slate for each tier','Short Totems\n\nAll tiers have short variants!\n\nSame recipe but leave the top row empty.\n\nDisplays items at eye-level instead of 2 blocks high.','Range Display\n\nPower a totem with redstone to see its range!\n\nWorks with:\n- Lever (toggle)\n- Torch (always on)\n- Redstone Block\n- Powered wire\n- Button (temporary)\n\nRed particles show the effect area!','Configuration\n\nCustomize settings in-game:\n\n/data get storage rituals:config\n\n/data modify storage rituals:config <key> set value <value>\n\n/function rituals:config/reload','Helpful Commands\n\n/function rituals:help\nShows help menu\n\n/function rituals:give/all\nGet all totem items\n\n/function rituals:give/guidebook\nGet another book','Advanced Tips\n\n- Higher tiers have larger ranges\n- Sentry ritual has 2x range\n- Break totem to retrieve it\n- Rituals last 30 seconds\n- Default: 1 totem required\n- Max distance: 32 blocks','Multi-Totem Mode\n\nWant to require multiple totems?\n\n/data modify storage rituals:config min_totems_required set value 3\n\n/function rituals:config/reload\n\nTotems must be within 32 blocks of each other.','Happy Ritualing!\n\nMay your totems shine bright and your rituals be powerful!\n\nFor more info, see README.md in the datapack folder.\n\n- Ancient Ritualist']}] 1
